text: Shanhe Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Shuangyang District, Changchun, Jilin, China. , it has 2 residential communities and 25 villages under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Jilin == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Jilin Category:Changchun
